title: "axiom-explorer: an LLM-assisted harness for cross-search over modern axiomatic seeds in mathematics, with one case study (condensed classifying anima envelope)"
version: "v1.0-preprint"
doi: "10.5281/zenodo.20184068"
date-released: "2026-05-14"
authors:
